Docker: Docker is a platform for developing,shipping and running applications using a container based virtualization technique.
1. Runs the same operating system as the Host Os
2. This allows it to share a lot of host operationg system resources.
3. In order to achieve this they Originally used LXC(Linux Containers) but later moved to runC(akaLibContainer).

Docker Components:-

1. Docker Engine
2. Docker Hub
3. Docker Machine
4. Docker Compose
5. Docker Swarm
6. Kitematic

Docker Concepts:--

Docker Container
Docker Images
Docker Volumes
Docker commits/tags/push/pull
Docker command line (CLI)


